qaApiDemos.demoDesc: 国内自动退改签查询TRR运价.xml
qaApiDemos.request:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<OTA_AirReIssuePriceRQ>
	<POS>
		<Source>
			<airlinecode>CA</airlinecode>
			<iatacode>08385252</iatacode>
			<CityCode>BJS</CityCode>
			<PseudoCityCode>BJS191</PseudoCityCode>
		</Source>
	</POS>
	<ReIssueinfos>
		<ReIssueinfo>
			<FlightSegments>
				<!-- 新航段信息 -->
				<FlightSegment>
					<departure LocationCode="SHA" />
					<arrival LocationCode="PEK" />
					<equipment AirEquipType="330" />
					<marketingCarrier Code="CA" />
					<operationCarrier Code="CA" />
					<departureTime>2018-12-21 10:55</departureTime>
					<arrivalTime>2018-12-21 13:15</arrivalTime>
					<type>NORMAL</type>
					<flightno>CA1832</flightno>
					<cabin>Y</cabin>
					<actionCode>HK</actionCode>
				</FlightSegment>
			</FlightSegments>
			<!-- 原票号 -->
			<TicketNumber_Before>999-2070145641</TicketNumber_Before>
			<IsInfant>false</IsInfant>
			<PassName>ZHANG/XIAO</PassName>
			<InvoluntaryIdentifier>false</InvoluntaryIdentifier>
			<!-- 新预定的PNR -->
			<BookingReferenceID ID="KRDDMP" ID_Context="PNR" />
		</ReIssueinfo>
	</ReIssueinfos>
</OTA_AirReIssuePriceRQ>
